# Project Structure

Proflasher is a Next.js web application that generates language-specific Anki flashcards with AI assistance.

## Directory Structure

- [proflasher/src/app](mdc:proflasher/src/app): Next.js app router pages and API routes
- [proflasher/src/components](mdc:proflasher/src/components): React components used across the application
- [proflasher/src/lib](mdc:proflasher/src/lib): Core functionality and utilities
- [proflasher/src/styles](mdc:proflasher/src/styles): CSS and styling files
- [proflasher/src/scripts](mdc:proflasher/src/scripts): Utility scripts for the project
- [data](mdc:data): Storage for flashcard data (gitignored in actual repo)

## Key Files

- [proflasher/src/env.ts](mdc:proflasher/src/env.ts): Environment variable handling
- [proflasher/src/types.ts](mdc:proflasher/src/types.ts): TypeScript type definitions
- [proflasher/src/lib/ankiConnect.ts](mdc:proflasher/src/lib/ankiConnect.ts): Integration with Anki via AnkiConnect
- [proflasher/src/lib/cardModel/noteTemplates.ts](mdc:proflasher/src/lib/cardModel/noteTemplates.ts): Flashcard template definitions for different languages
